Usage: hilite_proto_model [-help] [-keep_existing_hilite]
                          [-type {flex_module flex_instgroup partition power_domain}] -reset  | -level <integer> | {[-min_level <integer>] [-max_level <integer>]}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-keep_existing_hilite     # Hilite in addition to existing hilited objects
                          # (bool, optional)
-level <integer>          # Level to hilite (int, optional)
-max_level <integer>      # Maximum level to hilite (int, optional)
-min_level <integer>      # Minimum level to hilite (int, optional)
-reset                    # Un-hilite hilited objects (bool, optional)
-type {flex_module flex_instgroup partition power_domain}
                          # Set types to hilite (default=flex_module
                          # flex_instgroup) (enum_list, optional)